<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Special Islamic Days - Ummah Hub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/special-days.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    
    <main>
        <div class="decorative-pattern pattern-top-right"></div>
        <div class="decorative-pattern pattern-bottom-left"></div>
        
        <section class="special-days-container">
            <h2>Special Islamic Days</h2>
            <p>Stay informed about important Islamic dates, celebrations, and commemorations throughout the year. Our calendar helps you track significant days in the Islamic calendar.</p>
            
            <iframe 
                class="islamic-calendar-widget fade-in"
                scrolling="no" 
                src="https://www.islamicfinder.org/specialislamicdays">
            </iframe>

            <div class="islamic-info">
                <div class="info-card fade-in">
                    <h3>Ramadan</h3>
                    <p>The holy month of fasting, prayer, reflection and community. A time when Muslims worldwide fast from dawn to sunset.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card fade-in">
                    <h3>Eid ul-Fitr</h3>
                    <p>The festival of breaking the fast, celebrated at the end of Ramadan with special prayers, family gatherings, and charitable giving.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card fade-in">
                    <h3>Eid ul-Adha</h3>
                    <p>The festival of sacrifice, commemorating Prophet Ibrahim's devotion to Allah and marking the end of Hajj.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-card fade-in">
                    <h3>Hajj</h3>
                    <p>The annual Islamic pilgrimage to Makkah, a mandatory religious duty for Muslims that must be carried out at least once in their lifetime by those who are physically and financially capable.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
